item.title: CVE-2019-6630|2024-08-04T20:23:22.040Z -- f5 -- f5%20ssl%20orchestrator
item.description: On F5 SSL Orchestrator 14.1.0-14.1.0.5 and 14.0.0-14.0.0.4, undisclosed traffic flow may cause TMM to restart under certain circumstances.

item.title: CVE-2019-6627|2024-08-04T20:23:22.166Z -- f5 -- f5%20ssl%20orchestrator
item.description: On F5 SSL Orchestrator 14.1.0-14.1.0.5, on rare occasions, specific to a certain race condition, TMM may restart when SSL Forward Proxy enforces the bypass action for an SSL Orchestrator transparent virtual server with SNAT enabled.
